attributes.title: Someone with tiny hands made this app
attributes.review: Took way too long to download. When I answered some of the demographic questions, it told me “CONGRATULATIONS! YOU CHOSE RIGHT!!!!” Can you guess which one? Then there was this weird diatribe where the app recommended I watch several hours of InfoWars a day, before quickly diverting to the topic of North Korea and how the app sent a copy of “Rocketman” by Elton John to KJ.

attributes.title: This app took all my storage.
attributes.review: As soon as I downloaded the app, I got all set up, and then I started noticing that my storage was very full. Before, I had a ton of storage left, but when I got this app, it was literally sucked away. I do not recommend this app for anyone of any age or anything. I wouldn’t even give it one star, I’d give it zero.
